headline: M&T Bank Corporation Announces First Quarter Common Stock Dividend
summary: M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE:MTB) announced that it has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.50 per share on its common stock. The dividend will be payable March 31, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business on March 2, 2026.
